Package: altreplicate
Title: Compact representation of replication
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Jean-Romain", "Roussel", email = "jean-romain.roussel@ulaval.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: An implementation of compact repetition vectors using the ALTREP framework. rep(x, n) 
    allocates n blocks of memory. alt_rep(0, n) allocates only two values to store the same vector.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LinkingTo: Rcpp (>= 0.12.18.3)
Imports: 
    Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Suggests: tinytest
